{"tha-ap406:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap406:0.2":"Metteyyavagga ","tha-ap406:0.3":"Dhotakattheraapadana ","tha-ap406:1.1":"“Ganga bhagirathi nama, ","tha-ap406:1.2":"himavanta pabhavita; ","tha-ap406:1.3":"Hamsavatiya dvarena, ","tha-ap406:1.4":"anusandati tavade. ","tha-ap406:2.1":"Sobhito nama aramo, ","tha-ap406:2.2":"gangakule sumapito; ","tha-ap406:2.3":"Tattha padumuttaro buddho, ","tha-ap406:2.4":"vasate lokanayako. ","tha-ap406:3.1":"Tidasehi yatha indo, ","tha-ap406:3.2":"manujehi purakkhato; ","tha-ap406:3.3":"Nisidi tattha bhagava, ","tha-ap406:3.4":"asambhitova kesari. ","tha-ap406:4.1":"Nagare hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap406:4.2":"vasami brahmano aham; ","tha-ap406:4.3":"Chalango nama namena, ","tha-ap406:4.4":"evamnamo mahamuni. ","tha-ap406:5.1":"Attharasa sissasata, ","tha-ap406:5.2":"parivarenti mam tada; ","tha-ap406:5.3":"Tehi sissehi samito, ","tha-ap406:5.4":"gangatiram upagamim. ","tha-ap406:6.1":"Tatthaddasasim samane, ","tha-ap406:6.2":"nikkuhe dhotapapake; ","tha-ap406:6.3":"Bhagirathim taranteham, ","tha-ap406:6.4":"evam cintesi tavade. ","tha-ap406:7.1":"‘Sayam patam tarantame, ","tha-ap406:7.2":"buddhaputta mahayasa; ","tha-ap406:7.3":"Vihesayanti attanam, ","tha-ap406:7.4":"tesam atta vihannati. ","tha-ap406:8.1":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","tha-ap406:8.2":"buddho aggo pavuccati; ","tha-ap406:8.3":"Natthi me dakkhine karam, ","tha-ap406:8.4":"gatimaggavisodhanam. ","tha-ap406:9.1":"Yannuna buddhasetthassa, ","tha-ap406:9.2":"setum gangaya karaye; ","tha-ap406:9.3":"Karapetva imam kammam, ","tha-ap406:9.4":"santarami imam bhavam’. ","tha-ap406:10.1":"Satasahassam datvana, ","tha-ap406:10.2":"setum karapayim aham; ","tha-ap406:10.3":"Saddahanto katam karam, ","tha-ap406:10.4":"vipulam me bhavissati. ","tha-ap406:11.1":"Karapetvana tam setum, ","tha-ap406:11.2":"upesim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap406:11.3":"Sirasi anjalim katva, ","tha-ap406:11.4":"imam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap406:12.1":"‘Satasahassassa vayam, ","tha-ap406:12.2":"datva karapito maya; ","tha-ap406:12.3":"Tavatthaya mahasetu, ","tha-ap406:12.4":"patigganha mahamune’. ","tha-ap406:13.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap406:13.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap406:13.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap406:13.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap406:14.1":"‘Yo me setum akaresi, ","tha-ap406:14.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap406:14.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap406:14.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap406:15.0":"4.1. Setudanaanisamsa ","tha-ap406:15.1":"Darito pabbatato va, ","tha-ap406:15.2":"rukkhato patitopiyam; ","tha-ap406:15.3":"Cutopi lacchati thanam, ","tha-ap406:15.4":"setudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap406:16.1":"Virulhamulasantanam, ","tha-ap406:16.2":"nigrodhamiva maluto; ","tha-ap406:16.3":"Amitta nappasahanti, ","tha-ap406:16.4":"setudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap406:17.1":"Nassa cora pasahanti, ","tha-ap406:17.2":"natimannanti khattiya; ","tha-ap406:17.3":"Sabbe tarissatamitte, ","tha-ap406:17.4":"setudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap406:18.1":"Abbhokasagatam santam, ","tha-ap406:18.2":"kathinatapatapitam; ","tha-ap406:18.3":"Punnakammena samyuttam, ","tha-ap406:18.4":"na bhavissati vedana. ","tha-ap406:19.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap406:19.2":"hatthiyanam sunimmitam; ","tha-ap406:19.3":"Tassa sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap406:19.4":"nibbattissati tavade. ","tha-ap406:20.1":"Sahassassa vatajava, ","tha-ap406:20.2":"sindhava sighavahana; ","tha-ap406:20.3":"Sayam patam upessanti, ","tha-ap406:20.4":"setudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap406:21.1":"Agantvana manussattam, ","tha-ap406:21.2":"sukhitoyam bhavissati; ","tha-ap406:21.3":"Vehasam manujasseva, ","tha-ap406:21.4":"hatthiyanam bhavissati. ","tha-ap406:22.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap406:22.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap406:22.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap406:22.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap406:23.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap406:23.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap406:23.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap406:23.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap406:24.1":"Aho me sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap406:24.2":"jalajuttamanamake; ","tha-ap406:24.3":"Tattha karam karitvana, ","tha-ap406:24.4":"pattoham asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap406:25.1":"Padhanam pahitattomhi, ","tha-ap406:25.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap406:25.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap406:25.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap406:26.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap406:26.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap406:26.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap406:27.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap406:27.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap406:27.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap406:28.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap406:28.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap406:28.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap406:29.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dhotako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap406:30.1":"Dhotakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}